# L2 Switch
## Basic setup
```
en
conf t
hostname <Hostname>
enable secret <security>
username <security> secret <security>
line con 0
logging synch
login local
line vty 0 4 
logging synch
login local
no ip routing
exit
wr mem
!
```
## Per VLAN
```
vlan <VLAN ID>
name <Name>
exit
!
```
## Per SVI
```
interface vlan <VLAN ID>
description rmt_mgmt
ip address <IP> <Subnet>
shut
no shut
exit
!
```
## PER ACCESS
```
int <interface>
desc <desc>
switchport mode access 
switchport access vlan <vlan>
spanning-tree portfast
spanning-tree bpduguard Enable
shut
no shut
exit
!
```
## Per Trunk
```
int <interface>
desc <Description>
switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
**keep in mind this isnt needed on non-legacy equipment ^ **
switchport trunk allowed vlan <VLAN ID>,<VLAN ID>
switchport mode trunk
no spanning-tree portfast
shut
no shut
exit
!
```
## If auto duplex failure
```
conf t
int <port>
no negotiation auto
duplex <half|full|auto>
exit
```
## Port Channels
```
int port-channel <ID>
switchport trunk ecapsulation dot1q
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan <ID,ID>
exit
int <INT range>
switchport trunk ecapsulation dot1q
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan <ID,ID>
Channel-group <ID> mode <active|passive>
!
```

test

